long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
"Aliexpress Search by Image Plus"  extension is designed to enhance your shopping experience on Aliexpress. With this extension, you can easily search for products on Aliexpress using images. Whether you have a direct image link or want to upload an image from your device, "Aliexpress Search by Image Plus" makes it effortless to find similar or identical items on Aliexpress.

Features:

Image Link Search: Simply paste the URL of an image.
Image Upload: Upload images directly from your device to initiate a search for similar products on Aliexpress.
